<h3 class="title"><span>Young Book Club (YBC) - The English Department</span></h3>
	<br>
	<p>The YBC will meet twice a month in small group discussion at a different venue. This club will be open for grades 11 and 12 only. The main goal of this club would be to have participant read assigned novel/play/book and discuss it using their talents and imagination in dealing with some of the following areas: explanatory notes on a valuable personal qualities, character sketch of an important person, a description of significant events, and a memoir of a noteworthy events. Several skills will be gained during this time, including focusing and planning, drafting, dealing with real life situations and publishing and evaluating.</p>
</div>